{"tid":536311,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[tbb豬肉獎]寫低下你認為應該拎獎嘅人","createTime":"2018-01-21T16:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T01:55:28.000Z","uid":35870,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b3ef5837c2a64843bd00670be8fffb337b604a15","tid":536311,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"最佳劇集:誇世代<br />\n不解釋(降魔的其實都好睇，但誇世代個種規模真係屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n視帝: 陳豪<br />\n陳豪係誇世代嘅表現真係好出色，唔係話馬明同王浩信差，但陳豪真係高幾班，而且我覺得甚至比起之前佢拎視帝溏心風暴1嘅表現更加好<br />\n如果唔計陳豪，王浩信其實應該上年EU拎，今年到馬明就perfect<br />\n<br />\n最佳男角色: 馬明<br />\n呢個實至名歸，唔洗解釋<br />\n<br />\n視后: 江美儀<br />\n係親親我好媽入面展現到咩叫演技，特別係同個女嘈架個幕，完全係屈機<br />\n總而言之，點都唔會係唐c wing囉，咩玩法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有宣圈，田蕊尼，江美儀，最後竟然係唐c wing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係最最最最最最唔合理嘅獎項！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n最喜愛女角色: Ali<br />\n係誇世代入面，第一次見到ali識做戲，之前佢d戲非常生硬，我仲覺得呢條友好煩做乜仲可以做戲，但今次誇世代直頭係突破，突然升左幾十個lv咁，完全係改觀，而且個角色都幾正<br />\n之於達哥就eerrrrrrr,我無乜意見，只係我覺人中意李佳芯多d<br />\n<br />\n最佳男配角: KC <br />\nwtf?陳山聰？<br />\n陳山聰唔係話差嘅，但同KC比，差d囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n心目中排名係KC/肥仔&gt;張振朗&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;陳山聰<br />\n肥仔係降魔的戲份唔多，但佢死左個一集，真係完美carry，特別係佢喊個一幕，你feel到咩係起雞皮，個種由電視傳去你身體，再直入你內心個種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飛躍進步男藝員:張振朗<br />\n其實何廣沛同張振朗我都覺得做得好好，好難揀<br />\n我個人覺得何廣沛一開頭都麻麻地，係之後越做越好，所以我揀張振朗，同埋何廣沛仲後生，大把世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女配角: 唔記得有咩人<br />\n朱晨麗？really?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錯morning真係好好J，真係好撚正，我個人認為而家成個大台最正都係呢條女，有樣有身材，殺死左幾多人嘅子孫(Ali moon呢d無身材sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n之但係，演技真係有待改進，同最佳女配角呢個title差幾條街！！！<br />\n繼最佳女主角之後，呢個係第二個頒得差嘅獎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋咩內地小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飛躍進步女藝員: Mayaane <br />\n佢做主持係唔錯<br />\n<br />\n最佳綜藝資訊節目: 3日2夜<br />\n其實拎獎個d都幾好嘅，不過3日2夜真係屈機(有無朱智賢director's cut版本洗出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n最佳廢老獎: Orange<br />\n夠膽講山頭文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然佢平時奶共，但今晚呢下係正<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全晚最乞人僧:<br />\n叻哥<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦，又唔係有實力，又串77，你憑咩？？<br />\n講下笑都唔得你唔好做幕前啦on9</span></span><br />\n<br />\n全晚最佳金句: 謙虛黎講你都算hill張"},{"pid":"f7ac425ee918133daee9f012c832a865c5fa34bc","tid":536311,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco